Most of the stuff in this chapter was done in the ../chef-repo folder to follow the book.

Outside of the git scope I had to 
==================================
1. Added "192.168.33.34 default-centos65" to /etc/hosts 
2. Added "192.168.33.35 node-centos65" to /etc/hosts
3. On node node-centos65 Added "192.168.33.34 default-centos65" to /etc/hosts

To get a connection to the server to work I had to scp the servers SSL cert to the .chef/trusted-certs folder
